"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-paris-olympics-harry-hepworth-bronze-b1174676.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  With one leg longer than the other, a dodgy back and a hip issue, the chances of Harry Hepworth winning anOlympic medalwere far fetched.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\", \"score\": 0.9999999999959073, \"rank\": 4.287743220676898e-12, \"text\": \"Hepworth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the youngster of the British team vaulted his way to a surprise bronze on Sunday ahead of his world champion teammate Jake Jarman in the process.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9932756184192981, \"rank\": 0.006670019016775046, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"score\": 0.9961737099119147, \"rank\": 0.003659629857446533, \"text\": \"Jake\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hepworth had been diagnosed with Legg-Calv\\u00e9-Perthes disease, which halts the growth of the hip bone, at the age of five and the hyperactive child was ordered to not to play any sport for three years.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\", \"score\": 0.9999999999959073, \"rank\": 4.287743220676898e-12, \"text\": \"Hepworth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Legg\\u2013Calv\\u00e9\\u2013Perthes_disease\", \"score\": 0.9999999999772626, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Legg-Calv\\u00e9-Perthes disease\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Legg\\u2013Calv\\u00e9\\u2013Perthes_disease\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Legg\\u2013Calv\\u00e9\\u2013Perthes_disease\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He recovered, took up gymnastics and immediately shone despite a four-centimetre differential between the length of his legs, and, more recently, despite the fact he suffered a stress fracture in his back in February.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It stopped him from vaulting for nearly a month, not that it showed during the competition.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To come away with a medal I do not even have the words for it right now,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it's just the start.\\\"\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At a time whereMax Whitlock, the elder statesman of the team is bowing out of the sport, Hepworth is one of a number of rising stars in the set-up.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\", \"score\": 0.9999999999959073, \"rank\": 4.287743220676898e-12, \"text\": \"Hepworth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Hepworth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His father was in the stands to watch him and he admitted he could hear him shouting but could not make out the words.\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He now plans to celebrate by getting his driving licence.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As he put it, \\\"If I can get a bronze medal, I should be able to pass my test.\\\"\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jarman had been one of the favourites for the vault gold but admitted he had been struggling for weeks with his second vault.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He landed it but took a step back, was marked down and dropped to fourth and just outside the medals in the process.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games  Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year  Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions  Winter escapes and activities to end the year in style  And yet it was still a first vault medal of a British man at anyOlympics, whose score of 14.949 put him behind gold medallist Carlos Edriel Yulo and Artur Davtyan, of Armenia.\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9932756184192981, \"rank\": 0.006670019016775046, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 2193, \"end\": 2211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Edriel Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 2234, \"end\": 2241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9588119747276604, \"rank\": 0.042957339187445626, \"text\": \"Armenia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No Filipino male had ever won an Olympic gold before yesterday, now it has two courtesy of Edriel Yulo, who was awarded a house as a reward for the first gold.\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2342, \"end\": 2346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.072582190149147e-25, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was unclear what might lie in wait for the second.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There was disappointment, though for Becky Downie on the uneven bars.\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2496, \"end\": 2508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Becky_Downie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Becky Downie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Becky_Downie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Becky_Downie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Downie had wept when she entered the arena for the first qualification competition after the ordeal she has undergone to get to her third Olympics 16 years after her first.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her brother died suddenly of an undiagnosed heart condition just before the Olympic trials for Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2799, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999994514111362, \"rank\": 5.361561716518169e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And she was one of the most senior gymnasts to speak out in the abuse row that overshadowed the sport in Britain.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2911, \"end\": 2918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9807241247406269, \"rank\": 0.019654384339359884, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She revealed weight shaming leading to injuries and insults, and also faced online abuse following her decision to speak out.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But come the final, having started well, she fell off the high bar and to her knees to end her medal hopes at the age of 32.\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3234, \"end\": 3243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9996227148855374, \"rank\": 0.00037716499797297746, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3334, \"end\": 3343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9996227148855374, \"rank\": 0.00037716499797297746, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3412, \"end\": 3420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brighton\", \"score\